## 🧩 Typical Recon Workflow

1. Start with passive recon (Amass, theHarvester)
2. Enumerate domains/subdomains
3. Fingerprint technologies (Wappalyzer)
4. Scan ports/services (Nmap)
5. Discover hidden content (Gobuster)
6. Analyze vulnerabilities (Nikto, Burp Suite)

